hanh-Chi%E1%BA%BFu/%E1%BB%A8c-T%E1%BA%A7n-Nga/poem-3A5S3Wzw-TaG82z7Wf4ReA">Ức Tần Nga - 憶秦娥</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Thanh-Chi%E1%BA%BFu/author-6q8syMJi1LKPt3rH8HfbQQ">Lý Thanh Chiếu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/V%C4%83n-th%C3%A1i-phong-l%C6%B0u/poem-PTBoGiZ0rQjiB-CvRgsN1w">Văn thái phong lưu - 文采風流</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Ph%C3%BAc-L%C3%A2m/Vi%E1%BB%85n-s%E1%BA%A7m-y%C3%AAn-th%E1%BB%A5/poem-LDmfQTewSclZYOzwdMjUOw">Viễn sầm yên thụ - 遠岑煙樹</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Ph%C3%BAc-L%C3%A2m/author-kjKBPKP3VM3yjyBJUH1Xkw">Ngô Phúc Lâm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Di%E1%BB%85m/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-T%C3%A2y-H%E1%BB%93-t%E1%BB%A9c-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-F35JnP8kdQ4vTriFMrprvg">Xuân nhật Tây Hồ tức sự - 春日西湖即事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Di%E1%BB%85m/author-X_35N5JSG7X9VBxaNxbyhg">Trịnh Diễm</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
